  Gilbert, Donald (2010) Perfect(ing) Arthropod Genes with Next Gene Informatics
  4th annual Arthropod Genomics Symposium. Kansas State U.
  http://arthropods.eugenes.org/EvidentialGene/about/PerfectGenes2010.pdf 
