EvidentialGene is used by others in these reports

  Nakasugi K, Crowhurst R, Bally J, Waterhouse P (2014) 
  Combining Transcriptome Assemblies from Multiple De Novo Assemblers in
  the Allo-Tetraploid Plant Nicotiana benthamiana.
  PLoS ONE 9(3): e91776. doi:10.1371/journal.pone.0091776
  * independent review/comparison of Evigene and other tr assembly methods *
  
