  The Draft Genome Sequence of European Pear (Pyrus communis L. Bartlett). 
  PLoS ONE 9(4): e92644. doi:10.1371/journal.pone.0092644
  
  Shu Chen, J. Scott McElroy, Fenny Dane, and Eric Peatman (2014)
